  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Be between 18 and 70 years of age.

          -  Speak, understand, and read conversational English.

          -  Be a current patient of South Huntington Clinic recommended for behavioral health
             care.

          -  Have a smartphone and cell service plan, including voice and data, that meets the
             device requirements of the Mobile Sensing Platform.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Planning on permanently leaving Boston during the study period.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
